{"tid":1536733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我每日望到有人流血受傷被捕我心好痛","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:37:15.000Z","uid":95457,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"480210ffb65184913db72c36be837a7f560bfa12","tid":1536733,"uid":95457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"我唔係勇武 自知無資格評論佢地既決定<br />\n但每日都好卑微咁希望今日無人比人拉 無人流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家日日快閃示威 <br />\n班狗就好似：快d黎密d手 越黎越暴力<br />\n無論幾多cam影住佢地都毫不留手 <br />\n我知革命係要流血 但依家好似放緊血多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我提出唔到最可行方法 但依家局勢會唔會煲大一個百萬和理非遊行集會+跳閘大行動會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96449ff64fde0b2f33fbb1be6174d2bd0be473d4","tid":1536733,"uid":134107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"24e4286012622a71061452fb228db3d18638d1db","tid":1536733,"uid":88768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太子殺人犯</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1669 鍾國恩 警長<br />\n48958 李彼得 高級警員<br />\n54538 張文麟 高級警員<br />\n58248 梁智顯 高級警員 <br />\n52080 張達雄 高級警員<br />\n再加 8692 輔警 (未confirm)<br />\n<br />\n一定要推阿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推！！太子有片 六個殺人犯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f02025c3aa250b720196b3bf8d2a2373fd056e8","tid":1536733,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36ef9adc56a2ffd9d887027d6090dd5cd126d5b2","tid":1536733,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8fe83ed3c6af3a2c48d27fd711b9912f50e7ef1","tid":1536733,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:03.000Z","msg":",,,"},{"pid":"d985512dd847e7628d5ba47e1cb832aec7f2b47a","tid